snippet.title: Destiny of Heroes | Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Cut Trailer
snippet.description:
Destiny of Heroes is a twin-stick, squad-based shooter set in occupied Indonesia at the end of World War II. Fighting Dutch and Japanese colonizers, you will lead the struggle for independence, in a heroic struggle against foreign tyrants. Liberty or death! 

Instagram: instagram.com/nexvelentertainment/
Steam : store.steampowered.com/app/2906040/Destiny_of_Heroes/
